blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>徐臉都歪埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲有SUNNY都係<br />\n<br />\n少時好似得YURI同YOONA係冇整過</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nYuri就唔肯定，不過勝在身材好，又夠陽光<br />\nYoona就冇整啦，細個就係咁既樣，冇理由一出世就整<br />\n<br />\n其他成員多少都有整</blockquote><br />\n允兒真係好正，雖然五官唔係好精緻個種，但望落去好舒服，好清新，特別鍾意佢笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0456zh4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0456zh4.jpg&h=72aadcf4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/84P9855.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F84P9855.jpg&h=b7025c3e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/24/203323_9d4c09e92be8b7fc6f86b949d63b84bd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F24%2F203323_9d4c09e92be8b7fc6f86b949d63b84bd.jpg&h=dee89ba0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6qnXG69.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6qnXG69.jpg&h=d919707b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/24/203324_989e7c23f67522140d9cf5adea252e09.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F24%2F203324_989e7c23f67522140d9cf5adea252e09.jpg&h=0ca42a99&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n允兒係靚 個樣數一數二<br />\n但Yuri個種係好有魅力 好吸引人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nYuri在隊中身材真的最好!!!<br />\n允兒化了清新妝真係無敵手，但表演/濃妝就正如金希徹說的，比起不化來得顯老，根本不用這樣化"},{"pid":"e6ce6626090ab82102a785147989961c04a0501b","tid":168631,"uid":80183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T13:40:12.000Z","msg":"g"},{"pid":"bdf3bfb869ef5088078869845b9671ed77377417","tid":168631,